<article id="post-80446" class="news-style animate_on_visible top-t-bottom post-80446 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-actualite category-gratuit tag-fep tag-pandemie tag-sans-abri" data-speed="300" data-delay="300" style="padding:0px;">
	
	<div class="grid-holder">

        <div class="grid-holder-inner">
	 
        	
            <div class="entry-media">
                <div class="overlay"></div>
                <div class="post-thumbnail">
    
                    <img src="https://www.reforme.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/town-2430571_1280-1-800x800.jpg" class="attachment-blog_entry size-blog_entry lazyload  wp-post-image" alt="tr&ecirc;ve hivernale" data-original="https://www.reforme.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/town-2430571_1280-e1594041029284-1-800x599.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px">
                </div><!-- .post-thumbnail --> 

            </div><!-- .entry-media -->

            <div class="content">

                <header class="entry-header animate_on_visible bottom-t-top" data-delay="100" data-speed="400">
                        
                    <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.reforme.net/actualite/2020/07/06/la-fin-de-la-treve-hivernale-inquiete-la-fep/" rel="bookmark">La fin de la tr&ecirc;ve hivernale inqui&egrave;te la FEP</a></h2>
                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
                
                <div class="animated-content animate_on_visible bottom-t-top" data-delay="300" data-speed="400">
                    		<div class="entry-content ">
			
			<p>En raison de la pand&eacute;mie, des milliers de personnes pr&eacute;caires ont pu conserver leur logement ou b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier d&rsquo;h&eacute;bergements d&rsquo;urgence, ce qui prendra fin le 10 juillet. Les associations r&eacute;clament des solutions p&eacute;rennes.</p>
			
		</div><!-- .entry-content -->                </div>

                <div class="entry-button animate_on_visible bottom-t-top" data-delay="500" data-speed="400">
